                    <section class="entry">
	                	<h1>Practicing ませんでした</h1>
<h4>&ldquo;It not knowing what to do, it&#8217;s doing what you know.&rdquo; <span style="color: #888888;">- Tony Robbins</span></h4>
<p>Now that you know all four verb conjugations, it&#8217;s time to put that knowledge to use. Just like the last practice page, I&#8217;m going to ask you questions. This time, though, you need to pay attention to whether the question is in past tense or present tense. For example, if I ask &#8220;did you eat sushi?&#8221; then you have to answer &#8220;yes I <em>ate</em> sushi&#8221; using past tense as well. You couldn&#8217;t respond to that question by saying &#8220;Yes I will eat sushi,&#8221; since that&#8217;s not answering anything. The goal of this practice is to get you to use all the verb conjugations as well as to help you notice when things are in present or past tense (since it&#8217;s important to know that kind of thing in a conversation!).</p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../../audio/2-8-41.mp3">a</a> Q. エッセイ　を　かきましたか？<br />
Did you write the essay? <a style="display:none;" id="ddetlink27792866" href="javascript:expand(document.getElementById('ddet27792866'))">Answer →</a>
<div class="ddet_div" id="ddet27792866"><script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript">expand(document.getElementById('ddet27792866'));expand(document.getElementById('ddetlink27792866'))</script></p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../../audio/2-8-42.mp3">a</a> A1. はい、エッセイ　を　かきました<br />
Yes, I wrote the essay</p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../../audio/2-8-43.mp3">a</a> A2. いいえ、エッセイ　を　かきませんでした<br />
No, I did not write the essay</div></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../../audio/2-8-44.mp3">a</a> Q. スーパー　を　でましたか？<br />
Did you exit the supermarket? <a style="display:none;" id="ddetlink1735623988" href="javascript:expand(document.getElementById('ddet1735623988'))">Answer →</a>
<div class="ddet_div" id="ddet1735623988"><script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript">expand(document.getElementById('ddet1735623988'));expand(document.getElementById('ddetlink1735623988'))</script></p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../../audio/2-8-45.mp3">a</a> A1. はい、スーパー　を　でました<br />
Yes, I exited the supermarket</p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../../audio/2-8-46.mp3">a</a> A2. いいえ、スーパー　を　でませんでした<br />
No, I did not exit the supermarket</div></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../../audio/2-8-47.mp3">a</a> Q. ぎゅうにゅう　を　のみますか？<br />
Do you drink milk? <a style="display:none;" id="ddetlink1926221563" href="javascript:expand(document.getElementById('ddet1926221563'))">Answer →</a>
<div class="ddet_div" id="ddet1926221563"><script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript">expand(document.getElementById('ddet1926221563'));expand(document.getElementById('ddetlink1926221563'))</script></p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../../audio/2-8-48.mp3">a</a> A1. はい、ぎゅうにゅう　を　のみます<br />
Yes, I drink milk</p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../../audio/2-8-49.mp3">a</a> A2. いいえ、ぎゅうにゅう　を　のみません<br />
No, I do not drink milk</div></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../../audio/2-8-50.mp3">a</a> Q. てがみ　を　おくりましたか？<br />
Did you send the letter? <a style="display:none;" id="ddetlink1158635611" href="javascript:expand(document.getElementById('ddet1158635611'))">Answer →</a>
<div class="ddet_div" id="ddet1158635611"><script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript">expand(document.getElementById('ddet1158635611'));expand(document.getElementById('ddetlink1158635611'))</script></p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../../audio/2-8-51.mp3">a</a> A1. はい、てがみ　を　おくりました<br />
Yes, I sent the letter</p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../../audio/2-8-52.mp3">a</a> A2. いいえ、てがみ　を　おくりませんでした<br />
No, I did not send the letter</div></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../../audio/2-8-53.mp3">a</a> Q. にほんご　を　べんきょうしますか？<br />
Do you study Japanese? <a style="display:none;" id="ddetlink205101395" href="javascript:expand(document.getElementById('ddet205101395'))">Answer →</a>
