<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../../audio/2-8-58.mp3">a</a> A2. えいご　を　べんきょうします<br />
I will study English</p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../../audio/2-8-59.mp3">a</a> A3. すうがく　を　べんきょうします<br />
I will study math</p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../../audio/2-8-60.mp3">a</a> A4. りか　を　べんきょうします<br />
I will study science</p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../../audio/2-8-61.mp3">a</a> A5. フランスご　を　べんきょうします<br />
I will study French</p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;">A6. ____________________ (your answer here) </div></p>
<p>It&#8217;s incredibly simple to use verbs in these ways, and just knowing these four conjugations will actually get you pretty far. Unfortunately, there are about a billion more verb conjugations coming up (mostly in season 4), so you&#8217;re not quite there yet. However, knowing the verbs (keep studying your lists) and knowing just these four conjugations is probably 50%. The other 50% will take a little longer, but that&#8217;s because it consists of a lot of smaller things.</p>
<p>Before moving on, I&#8217;ve also created a verb conjugation practice sheet which will help you to practice your conjugations as well as your verb vocabulary. At this point, you should feel pretty good about at least 80-90% of the verbs from this chapter and the previous chapter (if you don&#8217;t, study them! You&#8217;ll need them!).</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="woo-sc-ilink"><a class="download" href="../../../downloads/worksheets/verb-conjugation.pdf">Verb Conjugation Worksheet</a></span></p>
<div class="woo-sc-box tick   ">By finishing this page, you should have a pretty good understanding of ます, ました, ません, and ませんでした verb forms. You should be able to use them too, at least in simple sentences. Also, you should know most of your verb vocabulary, which basically means you know 95% of the verbs you&#8217;ll ever use. That&#8217;s pretty awesome, I think.</div>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="btn large" href="../8-7/index.html#top">← 後</a> <a class="btn large primary" href="../8-9/index.html#top">前 →</a></p>
